\c 12
\s Vapristi naVaRevhi
\p
\v 1 Zvino ava vapristi neVaRevhi vakwira naZerubhabheri mwanakomana waShearitieri naJeshuwa: Seraya, Jeremiya, Ezira;
\v 2 Amariya, Maruki, Hatushi;
\v 3 Shekaniya, Rehumi, Meremoti;
\v 4 Idho, Ginetoi, Abhiya;
\v 5 Mijamini, Maadhiya, Bhiriga;
\v 6 Shemaya naJoyaribhi, Jedhaya;
\v 7 Saru, Amoki, Hirikiya, Jedhaya. Ava misoro yevapristi neyehama dzavo pamazuva aJeshuwa.
\v 8 Uye VaRevhi: Jeshuwa, Bhinui, Kadhimieri, Sherebhia, Judha, Mataniya, vaiva pamusoro pekuvonga, iye nehama dzake.
\v 9 NaBhakibhukiya, naUni, hama dzavo, vakatarisana navo pazvirindo.
\p
\v 10 Zvino Jeshuwa wakabereka Joyakimu, Joyakimu akaberekawo Eriashibhi, Eriashibhi ndokubereka Joyadha.
\v 11 Zvino Joyadha wakabereka Jonatani, Jonatani ndokubereka Jadhuwa.
\v 12 Zvino pamazuva aJoyakimu vapristi, misoro yemadzibaba, vaiva: WekwaSeraya, Meraya; wekwaJeremiya, Hananiya;
\v 13 wekwaEzira, Meshurami; wekwaAmariya, Jehohanani;
\v 14 wekwaMaruki, Jonatani; wekwaShebhaniya, Josefa;
\v 15 wekwaHarimi, Adhina; wekwaMerayoti, Herikai;
\v 16 wekwa Idho, Zekariya; wekaGinetoni, Meshurami;
\v 17 wekwaAbhiya, Zikiri; wekwaMinyamini; wekwaMoadhiya, Piritai;
\v 18 wekwaBhiriga, Shamuwa; wekwaShemaya, Jehonatani;
\v 19 wekwaJoyaribhi, Matenai; wekwaJedhaya, Uzi;
\v 20 wekwaSarai, Karai; wekwaAmoki, Ebheri;
\v 21 wekwaHirikiya, Hashabhiya; wekwaJedhaya, Netaneri.
\p
\v 22 VaRevhi pamazuva aEriashibhi, Joyadha, naJohwanani, naJadhuwa, vakanyorwa vakava misoro yemadzibaba, nevapristi kusvika pava paushe hwaDhariusi muPerisiya.
\v 23 Vanakomana VaRevhi, misoro yemadzibaba, vakanyorwa pabhuku reMakoronike kusvika pamazuva aJohwanani mwanakomana waEriashibhi.
\v 24 Nemisoro yeVaRevhi: Hashabhiya, Sherebhiya, Jeshuwa mwanakomana waKadhimieri, nehama dzavo dzakatarisana navo, kurumbidza nekuvonga, zvichienderana nemurairo waDhavhidhi munhu waMwari, chirindo chakanangana nechirindo.
\v 25 Mataniya, naBhakibhukiya, Obhadhiya, Meshurami, Tarimoni, naAkubhi; varindi vemikova, vachirinda zvirindo pamatura emasuwo.
\v 26 Ava vaivako pamazuva aJoyakimu mwanakomana waJeshuwa, mwanakomana waJozadhaki, nepamazuva aNehemiya mutongi, naEzira mupristi munyori.
\s Rusvingo rweJerusarema runotsaurirwa Jehovha
\p
\v 27 Zvino pakutsaurira kwavo Jehovha rusvingo rweJerusarema, vakatsvaka VaRevhi kubva panzvimbo dzavo dzese, kuuya navo kuJerusarema, kuzoita kutsaura nemufaro, zvese nekuvonga uye nekuimba, makandira, mitengeranwa uye nembira.
\v 28 Zvino vanakomana vevaimbi vakaungana pamwe, zvese kubva kumapani akapoteredza Jerusarema nekumisha yevaNetofati,
\v 29 nepaBheti-Girigari, uye kubva paparuwa rweGebha neAzimavheti, nokuti vaimbi vava vazvivakira misha yakapoteredza Jerusarema.
\v 30 Zvino vapristi neVaRevhi vakazvichenesa, ndokuchenesa vanhu, nemasuwo, nerusvingo.
\p
\v 31 Zvino ndakakwidza misoro yaJudha pamusoro perusvingo, ndokugadza mapoka makuru maviri kuvonga mumidungwe, rimwe kurudyi pamusoro perusvingo kusvika kusuwo remupfudze.
\v 32 Zvino shure kwavo kwakafamba Hoshaya, nehafu yemisoro yaJudha,
\v 33 naAzariya, Ezira, naMeshurami,
\v 34 Judha, naBhenjamini, naShemaya, naJeremiya,
\v 35 nepavanakomana vavapristi vane hwamanda: Zekariya mwanakomana waJonatani mwanakomana waShemaya mwanakomana waMataniya mwanakomana waMikaya mwanakomana waZakuri mwanakomana waAsafi,
\v 36 nehama dzake: Shemaya, naAzareri, Mirarai, Girarai, Maai, Netaneri, naJudha, Hanani, vane zviridzwa zvaDhavhidhi munhu waMwari, uye Ezira munyori waiva pamberi pavo;
\v 37 uye nepasuwo repachitubu nepakatarisana navo, vakakwira nematanho eguta raDhavhidhi, nepamukwidza werusvingo, pamusoro peimba yaDhavhidhi, kusvikawo pasuwo remvura, kumabvazuva.
\v 38 Neboka repiri revekuvonga rakafamba rakanangana \add navo\add*, neni ndichiritevera, uye hafu yevanhu pamusoro perusvingo, pamusoro peshongwe yemavira emoto, kusvika parusvingo rwakapamhama,
\v 39 uye kubva pamusoro pesuwo raEfuremu, nepamusoro pesuwo rekare, nepasuwo rehove, neshongwe yaHananeri, neshongwe yaHamea kusvika pasuwo remakwai, ndokumira pasuwo revarindi.
\v 40 Mapoka ari maviri ekuvonga ndokumira muimba yaMwari, neni nehafu yevatariri ineni,
\v 41 nevapristi Eriakimu, Maaseya, Miniyamini, Mikaya, Erioenai, Zekariya, Hananiya, vane hwamanda,
\v 42 naMaaseya, naShemaya, naEriazari, naUzi, naJehohanani, naMarikiya, naErami, naEzeri. Zvino vaimbi vakaimbisisa, vana Jezirahiya mutariri.
\v 43 Zvino nezuva iro vakabaira zvibairo zvikuru ndokufara; nokuti Mwari waiva avafadza nemufaro mukuru; nevakadziwo nevana vakafara, kusvika mufaro weJerusarema wanzwikwa kure.
\p
\v 44 Zvino nezuva iro vamwe vakagadzwa pamusoro pemakamuri ezvinokosha, zvezvipo, zvezvezvibereko zvekutanga, zvezvegumi, kuunganidza maari zvinobva muminda yemaguta migove yevapristi neyeVaRevhi yaiva yatarwa nemurairo, nokuti Judha wakafarira vapristi naVaRevhi vaishumira.
\v 45 Zvino vese vaimbi nevarindi vemikova vakachengeta faniro yaMwari wavo, nefaniro yekuchenesa, zvichienderana nemurairo waDhavhidhi naSoromoni mwanakomana wake.
\v 46 Nokuti pamazuva akare aDhavhidhi naAsafi, kwaiva nemisoro yekuimba uye rwiyo rwekurumbidza nekuvonga kuna Mwari.
\v 47 Zvino Israeri wese pamazuva aZerubhabheri, nepamazuva aNehemiya vaipa migove yevaimbi nevarindi vemikova, nyaya yezuva pazuva rayo; ndokutsaurira VaRevhi, uye VaRevhi vaitsaurira vanakomana vaAroni.